<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,151,932]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,332,476,500]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific epithet, an adjective, refers to the short body hairs which are not longer than the diameter of median ocellus.
